subject: trompe l'oeil tiktoks
body:
1. these [trompe l'oeil tiktoks](https://www.tiktok.com/@vitakari?lang=en), which get me every time even though i know what to expect going in (a true and delightful accomplishment)

2. [weird story](https://thehustle.co/one-mans-quest-to-end-cheating-in-virtual-cycling/) about some dude who is really amped about people cheating in online bike racing. cannot imagine caring this much about anything much less [squints] leaderboards for online bike racing

3. [tim's dill pickle flavor chips](https://www.utzsnacks.com/pages/tims_snacks_products), which have been my go-to lately and have visible dill lines on them and are imo superior to kettle brand pickle chips (also a great option)
